resources.string: Inokutendera iwe kuti muka ari mudziyo kubudikidza kaviri tapping pamusoro ari sikirini.

Inokutendera iwe kuti batanidza USB namano. apo kusashanda mwe mudziyo Inyaya USB mabasa, vakadaro sezvo ADB uye MTP, chido kwete kuva zviripo kusvikira ichi ndiko remara kana ari mudziyo ndiko rebooted. kwete zvose USB mano chido kushanda.
Inowedzera ari utetsa pamusoro ari kubata sikirini saka unobatwa anogona kuva vakanyorwa apo akapfeka wakasonwa nejira.
Rino ari chepiri sim kadhi slots. ichi fanira kwete kuva kusashanda kunze kokuti ipapo ndiko munhu sim kadhi mu ari chepiri slots. (Kunoda Reboot!)

Izvi mabasa kumativi nyaya ne Snapchat, Instagram uye mwe Video kutsikisa Apps. tizvishandise ari google avc encoder pachinzvimbo pamusoro ari HW avc encoder. iwe Chivabvu vanoda kuti restart ari App kana restart ari mudziyo pamberi ichi marongero zvinotora zvazviri. ichi Chivabvu wo chikonzero vamwe Video kutsikisa Apps kwete kuti kushanda.
Maita iwe zvose nokuti iwe kutsigira!
